# Directions to L100 Alchemy Trainer (Slipendi, mob 6805)

say { "hello";
	smile %n;
	say Hello %n, how can I assist you?;
	}

say { "next trainer";
	chuckle;
	tell %n Getting to your next trainer is part of your training.;
	tell %n Round and round you go, to the circle you must go.;
	tell %n Buy a ticket aye that be!;
	tell %n In the mage guild past East Kings Way is he!;
	}

# Powerstone quest
# Created by _Unknown_
# Copyright 1998, SneezyMUD Development Team.  All rights reserved.

say { "powerstone";
	checktoggle 125;
	checkuntoggle 127;
	say Young one, I have no time to waste...;
	say on the questions of an apprentice.;
	say As you can see i have much to do here.;
	say I heard of <p>someone<z> seeking power...;
	say At the outskirts of the city of Grimhaven...;
	say perhaps he would teach you how to use the power.;
	toroom $n goes back to $s experiments.;
	}

say { "someone";
	checktoggle 125;
	checkuntoggle 127;
	say Yes, I hear this particular person...;
	say is leading a poacher's camp just outside of Grimhaven.;
	say That is all I know.;
	smile %n;
	}

# Galvanize quest
# Created by _Unknown_
# Copyright 1998, SneezyMUD Development Team.  All rights reserved.

say { "galvanize";
	checktoggle 122;
	checkuntoggle 124;
	say Hmm....the armor enhancing spell is very eluding...;
	say and I am too busy at the moment...;
	say to teach you the details of the spell.;
	say Find a battle mage to teach you...;
	say the proper procedure of it...;
	say the battle mages are very good...;
	say at protecting and enhancing their armor.;
	say One in particular was very good...;
	say I hear he resided in a village of short people.;
	say Just south of some playful faerie-folk.;
	}

